lead_paragraph: Ireland number eight Jamie Heaslip is a doubt for this year's Six Nations championship after suffering a head injury in Leinster's Pro12 game against the Ospreys, the BBC reported on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Ireland's Heaslip a Six Nations Doubt After Head Injury
